import React from 'react'
import * as RBS from 'react-bootstrap'

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <RBS.Navbar bg="light" variant="light" expand="lg">
                <RBS.Navbar.Brand href='#' >Modelo Digital</RBS.Navbar.Brand>
                <RBS.Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">
                    <RBS.Nav
                        className="mr-auto my-2 my-lg-0"
                        style={{maxHeight: '100px'}}
                        navbarScroll
                    >
                        <RBS.Nav.Link href="#action1">Home</RBS.Nav.Link>
                    </RBS.Nav>
                </RBS.Navbar.Collapse>
            </RBS.Navbar>
        </>
    )
}

export default Header
